
Vigoroth	 A normal type Pokémon

VIGOROTH is always itching and agitated 
to go on a wild rampage.  It simply can’t 
tolerate sitting still for even a minute. 
 This POKéMON’s stress level rises if 
it can’t be moving constantly. 

